quran[10{c,v,t}:
11,118,"be shak tera rab agar chahta to tamam insanon ko aik giroh bana sakta tha, magar ab to woh mukhtalif tareeqon hi par chaltay rahen ge"
11,119,"aur be raah rawaiyon se sirf woh log bachchen ge jin par tairay rab ki rehmat hai isi ( azaadi intikhab o ikhtiyar ) ke liye hi to is ne inhen peda kya tha aur tairay rab ki woh baat poori ho gayi jo is ne kahi thi ke mein jahannum ko jin aur ensaan, sab se bhar dun ga"
11,120,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh payghambaroon ke qissay jo hum tumhe sunaate hain, woh cheezein hain jin ke zariye se hum tumahray dil ko mazboot karte hain un ke andar tum ko haqeeqat ka ilm mila aur imaan laane walon ko nasiyaat aur baydaari naseeb hui"
11,121,"rahay woh log jo imaan nahi laatay, to un se keh do ke tum apne tareeqay par kaam karte raho aur hum apne tareeqay par kiye jatay hain"
11,122,injaam car ka tum bhi intzaar karo aur hum bhi muntazir hain
11,123,"asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch chhupa howa hai sab Allah ke qabza qudrat mein hai aur sara maamla isi ki taraf rujoo kya jata hai pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, to is ki bandagi kar aur isi par bhrosa rakh, jo kuch tum log kar rahay ho tera rab is se be khabar nahi hai"
12,1,"a, l-, ray yeh uss kitaab ki ayaat hain jo apna mudda saaf saaf bayan karti hai"
12,2,hum ne usay nazil kya hai quran bana kar arabi zabaan mein taakay tum ( ahal arab ) is ko achi terhan samajh sakuu
12,3,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum is quran ko tumhari taraf wahi kar ke behtareen perayamein waqeat aur haqayiq tum se bayan karte hain, warna is se pehlay to ( un chizon se ) tum bilkul hi be khabar thay"
12,4,"yeh uss waqt ka zikar hai jab yousuf ne apne baap se kaha"" abba jaan, mein ne khawab dekha hai ke gayarah setaaray hain aur Sooraj aur chaand hain aur woh mujhe sajda kar rahay hain """
